// CollapsibleDetails
// Renders a markdown <details>/<summary> block as a collapsible section.
// The summary line is always visible; clicking it toggles the body content.

FUNCTION CollapsibleDetails(summary, children, defaultOpen) -> JSX     EXPORT
  Manages isOpen state (defaults to defaultOpen prop).
  Renders summary as a clickable header with a chevron icon.
  Body content slides in/out based on isOpen.
